title: Value types: Strict field setting enforcement

labels.name: project:valhalla
labels.description: Used to track Project Valhalla related work

body:
JEP draft: https://openjdk.org/jeps/8350458
latest spec: https://cr.openjdk.org/~dlsmith/jep8350458/jep8350458-20250409/specs/strict-fields-jvms.html
<s>The latest spec draft for JEP 401 https://cr.openjdk.org/~dlsmith/jep401/jep401-20241030/specs/value-objects-jvms.html adds addition strict field support including:</s>
* allowing for non-final ACC_STRICT instance fields
* added rules to ensure strict fields are set before a super() call
* enhanced StackMapTable to express unset field flags
fyi @hangshao0
